      "description": "CFD-predicted hemolysis index compared against in-vitro MIH measurements at 6 L/min, 2500 RPM. Predicted MIH = 0.0019 g/100 L; measured MIH = 0.0024 g/100 L. Relative error 21%. No uncertainty quantification provided for this result."
    },
